resources.description:
URL param "action" must be provided. The values of this param are:

1. 'create' - create the server record in the master database.
2. 'script' - returns the installation script
3. 'install' - run the installation script on the client server. In this case "root_password" has to be provided in the request body.

All these works also with mandatory URL param 'sid' which is supposed to match ID of the target server

resources.description:
Requests a cloudstick-agent to restart one of the following services at the client server:
1. Apache
2. nginx
3. PHP

Hence, the "restart" query parameter must be set to "apache", "nginx", "php"; in case of "php", additional query param must be provided - "version", which is supposed to be set to the desired PHP FPM version, for instance 70.
resources.name: Restart web components
